      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior finish maintains a high gloss, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from standard use. Inside, the cabin is clean and odor-free; the leather upholstery is in great shape with only light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All power features, including the sunroof and heated seats, operate exactly as they should. Mechanically, the car is robust, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and recent oil service. The service history is documented, showing regular maintenance intervals were strictly followed. With ample tire tread remaining and a smooth-shifting transmission, this car is ready for the road with no immediate work required.",
